ygData.messageBody:
Well, in my opinion, it SHOULD take this long to get these bad boys. I've
played a warrior and a shaman. I KNOW the value of SOW... If everyone had
JBoots, the game would be toast. JBoots are one of the best items in the
game. And, of course, I'm shaded by my Shamanic Opinion....

Leod/Zantaer, Fennin Ro, SOK

-----Original Message-----
From: Doug Sorensen [mailto:belgarth_of_surefall@...]
Sent: Thursday, August 05, 1999 10:44 AM
To: EQCheats@onelist.com
Subject: Re: [EQCheats] ___JBoots___


From: Doug Sorensen <belgarth_of_surefall@...>

A necro friend said he just put in 48 hours to get
those boots. Haven't heard anything about reducing the
time. Could there be anti-camp zones like some other
mobs perhaps?

Belgarth
